8 SECTION 11. G.S. 143-442 reads as rewritten:
9 "§ 143-442. Registration.
10 (a) Every pesticide prior to being distributed, sold, or offered for sale within this State or
11 delivered for transportation or transported in intrastate commerce or between points within this
12 State through any point outside this State shall be registered in the office of the Board, and such
